    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><blockquote>
<h1 id="JS中Tab切换"><a href="#JS中Tab切换" class="headerlink" title="JS中Tab切换"></a>JS中Tab切换</h1><p><small>需要少许前端基础</small></p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h4 id="📕这是一篇教学，教大家如果使用js实现tab切换"><a href="#📕这是一篇教学，教大家如果使用js实现tab切换" class="headerlink" title="📕这是一篇教学，教大家如果使用js实现tab切换"></a>📕这是一篇教学，教大家如果使用js实现tab切换</h4><p><strong>效果如下⬇</strong><br><img src="/images/jx-1.png" alt="1"><br><img src="/images/jx-2.png" alt="2"><br><img src="/images/jx-3.png" alt="3"></p>
<h3 id="可以在网页中实现无需跳转或增加路由而切换页面"><a href="#可以在网页中实现无需跳转或增加路由而切换页面" class="headerlink" title="可以在网页中实现无需跳转或增加路由而切换页面"></a>可以在网页中实现无需跳转或增加路由而切换页面</h3><hr>
<p><strong>html5代码如下：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class="container"&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class="up"&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;li class="act"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;百度&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;新浪&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;淘宝&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;京东&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;网易&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class="down"&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div class="down-act"&gt;百度内容&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;新浪内容&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;淘宝内容&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;京东内容&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;网易内容&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<h2 id="★在上述代码的下面-amp-body的里面，引入js"><a href="#★在上述代码的下面-amp-body的里面，引入js" class="headerlink" title="★在上述代码的下面 &amp; body的里面，引入js"></a>★在上述代码的下面 &amp; body的里面，引入js</h2><p><em><strong>引入</strong></em></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src="[你自己创建的js文件名].js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<hr>
<h2 id="css代码如下⬇"><a href="#css代码如下⬇" class="headerlink" title="css代码如下⬇"></a>css代码如下⬇</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*{</span><br><span class="line">margin: 0;</span><br><span class="line">padding: 0;</span><br><span class="line">box-sizing: border-box;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">body{</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: gray;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.container{</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: white;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 500px;</span><br><span class="line">    height: 300px;</span><br><span class="line">    margin: 100px auto;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.up{</span><br><span class="line">    height: 50px;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.up ul li{</span><br><span class="line">    float: left;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 100px;</span><br><span class="line">    line-height: 60px;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.up ul li a{</span><br><span class="line">    font-size: 21px;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.act{</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: 2px solid black;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.down{</span><br><span class="line">    height: 200px;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    position: relative;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.down div{</span><br><span class="line">    position: absolute;</span><br><span class="line">    line-height: 110px;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    height: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    display: none;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line">.down div.down-act{</span><br><span class="line">    display: block;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<h2 id="★这里需要注意的是，你需要记得在head里引入css样式"><a href="#★这里需要注意的是，你需要记得在head里引入css样式" class="headerlink" title="★这里需要注意的是，你需要记得在head里引入css样式"></a>★这里需要注意的是，你需要记得在head里引入css样式</h2><hr>
<p>*** js代码如下⬇ ***</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var lis = document.querySelector(".up").querySelectorAll("li");</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">var divs = document.querySelector(".down").querySelectorAll("div");</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">for (var  i= 0; i &lt; lis.length; i++) {(</span><br><span class="line">    function(i){</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    lis[i].addEventListener("mouseenter",function(){</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        for (var k = 0; k &lt; lis.length; k++) {</span><br><span class="line">            lis[k].removeAttribute("class")</span><br><span class="line">            divs[k].removeAttribute("class")</span><br><span class="line">        }</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       lis[i].setAttribute("class","act")</span><br><span class="line">       divs[i].setAttribute("class","down-act")</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      })</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">}(i)</span><br><span class="line">)}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<h4 id="切记！去js官网寻找下载js的不同方式，最后记得插件里下载js的补全"><a href="#切记！去js官网寻找下载js的不同方式，最后记得插件里下载js的补全" class="headerlink" title="切记！去js官网寻找下载js的不同方式，最后记得插件里下载js的补全"></a>切记！去js官网寻找下载js的不同方式，最后记得插件里下载js的补全</h4><hr>
<h4 id="快去vs或者idea里实操吧✔"><a href="#快去vs或者idea里实操吧✔" class="headerlink" title="快去vs或者idea里实操吧✔"></a>快去vs或者idea里实操吧✔</h4>]]></content>
